20
00:01:48,940 --> 00:01:50,740
I'm here today...

21
00:01:52,540 --> 00:01:53,500
because of him.

22
00:01:57,140 --> 00:01:58,180
If I had jumped off

23
00:01:59,180 --> 00:02:00,700
the building that day...

24
00:02:04,260 --> 00:02:05,780
