27
00:02:31,140 --> 00:02:31,740
Got a moment?

28
00:02:33,260 --> 00:02:34,980
I'd like to recommend someone to you.

29
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:38,260
Fan, we've got work!

30
00:02:38,620 --> 00:02:39,420
Fan!

31
00:02:39,580 --> 00:02:40,660
Get up and come downstairs.

32
