Stop it. No need to shout.

34
00:02:46,940 --> 00:02:48,340
He barely gets to sleep in.

35
00:02:48,340 --> 00:02:49,220
Let him rest a bit longer.

36
00:02:49,220 --> 00:02:50,460
But he's already...

37
00:02:50,460 --> 00:02:51,660
It's not like he has a job

38
00:02:51,660 --> 00:02:52,860
or a company to go to anyway.

39
00:02:54,540 --> 00:02:55,140
Xiaoru,

40
00:02:55,860 --> 00:02:56,460
come here.

41
00:03:00,900 --> 00:03:01,820
Uncle Jia.

42
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:03,900
I need you to tell me

43
00:03:04,540 --> 00:03:06,420
exactly why he was fired.

44
00:03:06,780 --> 00:03:07,740
I've been thinking about it for days,

45
00:03:07,740 --> 00:03:08,740
