46
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:10,580
Come on, Uncle Jia.

47
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:11,460
What are you talking about?

48
00:03:11,660 --> 00:03:12,940
There's no way he got fired.

49
00:03:12,940 --> 00:03:13,700
Then why are you...?

50
