62
00:03:33,260 --> 00:03:33,780
Dad.

63
00:03:34,860 --> 00:03:35,580
You're up.

64
00:03:35,740 --> 00:03:36,980
Well, go freshen up.

65
00:03:36,980 --> 00:03:38,340
The baozi are still warm.

66
