96
00:04:22,140 --> 00:04:23,140
That's great!

97
00:04:23,180 --> 00:04:23,740
Fan,

98
00:04:23,980 --> 00:04:25,060
congratulations.

99
00:04:25,300 --> 00:04:26,380
Though my eyes may fail me,

100
