127
00:05:41,260 --> 00:05:41,900
Mo,

128
00:05:42,140 --> 00:05:43,780
Ms. Ling came in asking for sandwiches.

129
00:05:44,100 --> 00:05:45,060
We don't sell those, do we?

130
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:48,820
Blueberry and tuna sandwich.

131
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:54,180
If you ever want one,

132
00:05:54,340 --> 00:05:55,420
