133
00:05:55,780 --> 00:05:57,060
Order an hour in advance,

134
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:57,940
and I'll deliver it to your door.

135
00:05:58,020 --> 00:05:58,540
No.

136
00:05:58,980 --> 00:05:59,820
That won't be necessary.

137
00:06:01,460 --> 00:06:03,220
