♪Fish of the deep sea♪

167
00:07:30,940 --> 00:07:31,780
Not bad.

168
00:07:32,030 --> 00:07:33,260
♪Into dreams they glide♪

169
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:34,420
I bet you come here often.

170
00:07:35,870 --> 00:07:38,060
♪I hear you calling my name♪

171
00:07:38,060 --> 00:07:39,620
When I'm feeling down,

172
00:07:39,820 --> 00:07:41,060
