173
00:07:43,100 --> 00:07:44,300
It really helps me heal.

174
00:07:44,300 --> 00:07:45,500
♪Tears roll silently♪

175
00:07:45,500 --> 00:07:46,620
You'll get it once you try it.

176
00:07:46,620 --> 00:07:49,590
♪I want to reach out but I'm trapped♪

177
00:07:49,990 --> 00:07:53,100
♪In this desolate dream♪

178
00:07:53,100 --> 00:07:54,540
There are actually many places

179
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:56,060
like this.

180
00:07:57,140 --> 00:07:59,980
But you're always busy with work.

181
00:08:01,060 --> 00:08:03,060
You won't notice them
even if they're right in front of you.

182
00:08:04,370 --> 00:08:09,100
♪You'll always come closer with warmth♪

183
00:08:09,100 --> 00:08:09,820
Yeah.

184
00:08:11,310 --> 00:08:14,020
♪When the sun shines in♪

185
00:08:14,020 --> 00:08:15,740
That's why I gave myself a day off.

186
00:08:16,980 --> 00:08:18,380
I didn't go to the office or home,

187
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:20,260
but in the end,

188
00:08:21,420 --> 00:08:22,380
I had no place to go.

189
00:08:23,340 --> 00:08:24,500
But now you do.

190
00:08:24,990 --> 00:08:26,740
♪You took me away♪

191
