I don't intend to open this place

192
00:08:28,300 --> 00:08:29,380
to the public.

193
00:08:30,700 --> 00:08:32,620
It's reserved
for one special guest only.

194
00:08:32,950 --> 00:08:36,290
♪You told me not to give up♪

195
00:08:36,690 --> 00:08:38,020
