196
00:08:38,020 --> 00:08:39,980
Aren't you worried I'll steal your spot?

197
00:08:39,980 --> 00:08:43,140
♪Until I touch♪

198
00:08:43,140 --> 00:08:43,820
I'd love that.

199
00:08:44,940 --> 00:08:45,820
That way,

200
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:47,140
I'll know

201
00:08:47,140 --> 00:08:48,540
where to find you in the future.

202
00:08:48,540 --> 00:08:50,370
♪When the sky lights up♪

203
00:08:50,730 --> 00:08:54,210
♪There is warmth in the palm♪

204
00:08:54,330 --> 00:08:57,410
♪I see you waiting♪

205
00:08:57,970 --> 00:09:00,350
♪At the end of my dream♪

206
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:06,900
Is it because of Yijing?

207
00:09:13,860 --> 00:09:15,020
When did she and Jia Fan...

208
00:09:15,020 --> 00:09:16,540
♪Only when I fall to the bottom♪

209
00:09:16,540 --> 00:09:17,620
