210
00:09:17,620 --> 00:09:20,020
♪Do I understand the meaning of love♪

211
00:09:20,020 --> 00:09:21,100
After Fan joined the company.

212
00:09:21,190 --> 00:09:27,060
♪You'll always come closer with warmth♪

213
00:09:27,260 --> 00:09:28,300
So you knew all along?

214
00:09:28,300 --> 00:09:31,210
♪When the sun shines in♪

215
00:09:31,250 --> 00:09:35,260
♪You sharpen in my eyes♪

216
00:09:35,260 --> 00:09:36,900
