217
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:39,580
so you wouldn't find out.

218
00:09:39,580 --> 00:09:41,420
♪I saw it was you♪

219
00:09:41,810 --> 00:09:44,700
♪You took me away♪

220
00:09:44,770 --> 00:09:46,140
♪From the lonely dream♪

221
00:09:46,140 --> 00:09:47,660
You really are the one to count on.

222
00:09:49,770 --> 00:09:52,500
♪You told me not to give up♪

223
00:09:52,500 --> 00:09:54,100
