228
00:10:09,340 --> 00:10:10,780
Until she met Jia Fan.

229
00:10:12,420 --> 00:10:14,100
She's still as brave as ever.

230
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:16,300
Why are you here?

231
00:10:16,300 --> 00:10:17,420
She never hesitates or holds back.

232
00:10:17,580 --> 00:10:18,580
I'm here to pick up my girlfriend,

233
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:19,900
