242
00:10:34,020 --> 00:10:34,860
Of course, I did.

243
00:10:34,900 --> 00:10:36,260
Everyone at the market has one.

244
00:10:36,260 --> 00:10:36,940
My treat.

245
00:10:37,540 --> 00:10:38,940
You're so nice to me.

246
00:10:38,940 --> 00:10:40,620
Thank you, Mr. Jia, for your support.

247
00:10:41,060 --> 00:10:42,420
You're most welcome.

248
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:44,700
Just take me out for a meal.

249
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:45,580
Sure,

250
00:10:45,740 --> 00:10:46,660
