283
00:13:27,980 --> 00:13:30,300
Actually, you've done well enough.

284
00:13:30,940 --> 00:13:32,580
Yijing knows that deep down.

285
00:13:33,460 --> 00:13:35,140
Otherwise,
she wouldn't be suffering so much.

286
